#

Pan-Seared Salmon with Honey Garlic Glaze

$25
500 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

fishsoy

Dietary Tags:

gluten-freehigh-protein

Tags:

seafooddinnereasyhealthy

Description

Juicy salmon fillet glazed with a sweet and savory honey garlic sauce, served with seasonal vegetables.

Ingredients

  • salmon fillets: 2 (6 oz)
  • honey: 3 tbsp
  • soy sauce: 2 tbsp
  • garlic: 3 cloves, minced
  • olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • broccoli florets: 1 cup
  • carrots, sliced: 1 cup
